## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.
##
## This .gitignore is for a standard Blazor WebAssembly / .NET project.

# Build results
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/

# Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Rider
.idea/

# Visual Studio Code
.vscode/

# Web Files
wwwroot/TSFamilyFun.styles.css
wwwroot/TSFamilyFun.bundle.scp.css

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
